y</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Magician vs Sk/cleric combo</span><hr size=1> I fully expect not to prevail, but does anyone have suggestions on how a lv 54 magician would manage a combination of a lv 47 SK and lv 49 cleric?<br>
<br>
With a 30 sec buff period, I can't prevent the cleric buffing the SK. Clerics nukes are magic based and SK's dots are desise based, so high magic and desise saves would be preferrable. Also, will a high magic resist help with HT and taps? <br>
<br>
I expect more than half the battle is won IF one of them goes down, especially if the pet still lives.<br>
<br>
I have run 3 which helps a lot, but they may have Jboots.<br>
<br>
