<br>
I'd definitely use the water pet for this, even if rooted or blinded it nukes quite a lot, the other pets aren't going to do as much damage if their mobility is gone, except maybe fire which will waste time casting spells that are easy to resist.<br>
<br>
as sk, I would save ht until the cleric got a good dd in, which would probably finish the mage.<br>
